INSERT INTO edu_course_exercise (id, question_type, course_id, content, easy_error, source, dw_checked, is_pk) VALUES ('1811410', '15', '90909090', '<p>已知抛物线的顶点在原点、开口向右、焦点为 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=BlkXDnmzWHxe4M6E9LlofQ%3D%3D" />，过焦点 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=BlkXDnmzWHxe4M6E9LlofQ%3D%3D" /> 且倾斜角等于 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=z%2FkiPqk1fQtjrvX%2FQ%2BD9lw%3D%3D" /> 的直线与抛物线相交于<img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=2RUiDci9WF8R0kLIZXKikQ%3D%3D" /> 两点，分别过点 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=2RUiDci9WF8R0kLIZXKikQ%3D%3D" /> 作准线 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=O1PzqaL1%2BAfC%2FNERqj1Zew%3D%3D" /> 的垂线，垂足分别是 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=VcrxcYziFCqtoEZ5mXhdpQ%3D%3D" />，若四边形 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=mH3XTehvonAZCNs76DQlQw%3D%3D" /> 的面积等于 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=9YUFuej7b4FhBhVnxLnTkA%3D%3D" />，求此抛物线的方程.</p><p>  若将此问题作为一个教学例题，请你认真阅读下面的教学设计提纲，并简答其中包含的主要数学思维方法、知识要点及新课程理念.</p><p>（1）组织学生认真阅读题目，并画出示意图；</p><p>（2）引导学生提出解决问题的基本思路：</p><p>  将抛物线方程设为 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=pSUW4HfEDL6wM9VJc3l7Bn8cJZq7HUQsco6m0dKJ2ac%3D" />，然后根据条件求出系数 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=QPadlhZ3vYN%2FHi29gpTrFw%3D%3D" />.</p><p>（3）让学生对题目信息进行分析和处理，并写出抛物线 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=bAmPePWFsHFi0Au9TPYTIg%3D%3D" /> 的焦点坐标、准线方程及直线 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=cHJ4KDAad01mWuGaiQQpfA%3D%3D" /> 的方程 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=76re%2BAPaqeYtnEPEg4tSqnoCSvKdxX75YIOt%2BTLbDzw%3D" />；</p><p>（4）引导学生去发现使用条件“四边形 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=Ntu93zITeX6ZZAdBrCfFOw%3D%3D" /> 的面积等于 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=9YUFuej7b4FhBhVnxLnTkA%3D%3D" />”的核心问题是能用 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=dSWbQCTjdbLxKy7q0ps2gg%3D%3D" /> 表示<img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=IrcOZZUhFmM2aU%2B5S%2FGeBg%3D%3D" />和 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=q7Ikhq%2BueghY7Ha%2BJpP3hw%3D%3D" />；并注意到 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=TdLEXiIafSIroOPznynDDzOP%2BwzbiXa36SRbwgx8EUs%3D" />；</p><p>（5）引导学习成绩处于中间层次的学生，在回顾弦长公式的基础上，假设坐标 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=n4ME3%2BjGgkLcTudTIN2EGq39yLYXuTpTX2qkVwhh1dw%3D" />，得出 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=oEkXH1FVuw4mb5nEEPYJCYCJGA28fSk5e36arbxvp3zmuC0Il9rSk7Ofsoej907RGj%2FwAoaouP5XiAzdyH76CA%3D%3D" />；</p><p>（6）提出问题：怎样才能求出 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=pKHfVOsbKglTS%2BzQkroMbg%3D%3D" /> 和 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=g%2Ba4oJ%2BVR0QN9SgqyglMRA%3D%3D" />？学生通过讨论总结，让学习较好的同学交流如下求解过程：</p><p>  由 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=9PdFkyNZN0jrsDSPEdYMEzY9UWAsbbrRO0XTSsMcbjOybt9WJFSt5RlTYf5vgDNb85nI9%2FIE1kXgRqhK5CG9qV5Z68eLtTxPLpnnahancqk%3D" /> 消去 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=Hz6y44ELFVLLNrLVhO3CQA%3D%3D" /> 得 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=AjJ9YD%2BMMb5FKjYgqvmn31ScHtBoW34lcqkupG%2FsdWp9lUiUXNbWlOM9JGz38UmY" />，从而有</p><p>  <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=Q8mlrxsiKIZryIZO4MGc7wdXR5%2FK%2BLLHX7v0eMUSGU6u3ZKwV8d4q6nQAgG8dTrTgNhPyII7OeJDeyr%2FbpZB5g%3D%3D" /></p><p>  于是 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=JpF2Z929n%2Ba4nmRtlLB%2BDMJGdrTc%2FESGs17eZz%2F%2FRqQuuyu7RbBKfAJLoToWJL3c9bjJqSdsDAmjFdR1nPopZQ%3D%3D" /></p><p>  <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=H5v6ZFCSYYVMrxHztJF5SJssZ9a8BQjoL7ZG0OnmCf%2BSm8TkuIM46yi5%2B0POeSGeHcPl8P5BrF20lASOg5hhyg%3D%3D" /></p><p>  所以 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=GWRstmeW8%2FWm0ruPCDbq2jwsRoeYfxnTlaSnUeE5dg8%3D" /></p><p>（7）让成绩靠后的同学交流求抛物线方程的最后步骤：</p><p>  将 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=GWRstmeW8%2FWm0ruPCDbq2jwsRoeYfxnTlaSnUeE5dg8%3D" />代入 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=E29t0uemX0glusb%2BrwLk5o%2BK4jFDcOTjCHQsVBq%2BsZ2d%2BKuymwnXgbKa%2B05%2FPeer" />，得：<img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=n2BtQOYBxm%2BJ6WlsjLSk8g%3D%3D" /></p><p>  所以抛物线方程 <img flag="tex" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/planet/accessories/formulas?latex=2UB5V4vY%2FPW4htlsIRhuoQ%3D%3D" /></p><p><img width="417px" height="461px" src="https://fb.fbstatic.cn/api/tarzan/images/156020c4936e373.jpg?width=700" /></p>', '', '2012年江西省教师招聘考试《高中数学》题第43题', '0', '0');
